dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jeremy Patterson. May I have your name, please?
Thank you, Evelyn. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Yes, it's eight seven six two one.
Great, thank you. And could you confirm the make and model of your vehicle for verification purposes?
Sure, it's a two zero one eight Toyota Corolla.
Thank you for confirming, Evelyn. How can I assist you today with your Old Stone Auto Insurance policy?
I would like to add a new driver to my policy.
Of course, Evelyn. We can assist with that request. I will need a bit more information to complete the process. Please provide the new driver's full name and date of birth.
The new driver's name is Michael Johnson and his date of birth is April fifth, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you for the information, Evelyn. We will process the request to add Michael Johnson as a driver to your policy. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you for your help, Jeremy.
You're welcome, Evelyn. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
